headline: Clorox to Present at Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference
summary: The Clorox Company (NYSE: CLX) today announced that Chief Financial Officer Luc Bellet will participate in a fireside chat at the Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference on Tuesday, Dec. 2, 2025, in New York City.
